# Configuration Reference

## `da`

| Field | Value |
| --- | --- |
| Rust config | `DataAvailabilityConfig` |

### `da.client`

| Field | Value |
| --- | --- |
| Type | string tag with variants |

| Value | Rust variant | Default | Aliases | Description |
| --- | --- | --- | --- | --- |
| `None` | `DataAvailabilityConfig::None` | yes |  | Do not use data availability anywhere. |
| `ObjectStore` | `DataAvailabilityConfig::ObjectStore` |  |  | Store data in an object store. |

## `da`

| Field | Value |
| --- | --- |
| Rust config | `ObjectStoreConfig` |

### `da.type`

| Field | Value |
| --- | --- |
| Type | string tag with variants |
| Tag | `da.client` == `ObjectStore` |

| Value | Rust variant | Default | Aliases | Description |
| --- | --- | --- | --- | --- |
| `local` | `ObjectStoreConfig::Local` | yes |  | Stores object locally as files. |
| `s3` | `ObjectStoreConfig::S3` |  |  | Stores objects in AWS S3. |
| `gcs` | `ObjectStoreConfig::Gcs` |  | `google`, `google_cloud` | Stores objects in Google Cloud Storage. |

### `da.path`

| Field | Value |
| --- | --- |
| Type | `string`; filesystem path |
| Rust type | `PathBuf` |
| Tags | `da.client` == `ObjectStore` && `da.type` == `local` |
| Default | `"."` |

Path to the root directory.

### `da.bucket_name`

| Field | Value |
| --- | --- |
| Type | `string` |
| Rust type | `String` |
| Tags | `da.client` == `ObjectStore` && `da.type` == `gcs` |

Bucket to put objects into.

## `da`

| Field | Value |
| --- | --- |
| Rust config | `S3Config` |

### `da.bucket_name`

| Field | Value |
| --- | --- |
| Type | `string` |
| Rust type | `String` |
| Tags | `da.client` == `ObjectStore` && `da.type` == `s3` |

Bucket to put objects into.

### `da.region`

| Field | Value |
| --- | --- |
| Type | `string` |
| Rust type | `Option` |
| Type filtering | must not be empty, otherwise set to `null` |
| Tags | `da.client` == `ObjectStore` && `da.type` == `s3` |
| Default | `null` |

AWS availability region.
